{
  "texts": [
    "Such offline analysis may involve program dependency analysis, or simply control flow analysis of the passing / failing tests.",
    "Let us examine how the control flow analysis of passing / failing tests will proceed under the auspices of statistical fault localization.",
    "In such an approach, each statement 𝑠 in the program is given a suspiciousness score based on the occurrences of 𝑠 in the passing / failing tests.",
    "Constraint-based APR techniques also rely on fault localization to determine the line to be fixed.",
    "Once a fix line is decided, a repair constraint is then constructed."
  ]
}